<title>Táńirim meniń qalqanym РӘЖ91</title>
<key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.     Dm     C     Dm C
 Táńirim meniń qalqanym,
 Jasqansam bolar jartasym.
.     Gm      C         F    Dm
 // Ózińnen ózge eshkim joq, Áke,
.     Gm   C        Dm
 Kútemin kómek tek Senen. //

[V2]
 Táńirim meniń járdemshim,
 Kózimdi saǵan tigemin.
 // Qanatyńnyń astynda Áke,
 Qaýipsiz ómir súremin. //</lyrics>
</song>